name: @inkline/inkline
description: Inkline is the intuitive UI Components library that gives you a developer-friendly foundation for building high-quality, accessible, and customizable Vue.js 3 Design Systems.
author: Alex Grozav <alex@grozav.com>

scripts.prerelease:checks: npm run lint && npm run test && npm run e2e
scripts.prerelease:build: npm run build && npm run generate
scripts.e2e: npm run e2e:vite && npm run e2e:nuxt
scripts.integration:create: npm run integration:vite:create && npm run integration:nuxt:create
